txt.en: Siege engines and banners can be found in the encampment of Urûshoba.\n\nYou should destroy siege engines and banners.

Siege engines and banners can be found in the encampment of Urûshoba.\n\nYou should destroy siege engines and banners.

The Jangovar encampment of Urûshoba has been nothing but trouble for the people of the Dale-lands. Destroying the siege equipment and banners in Urûshoba should help push the Jangovar out of the Dale-lands.
The Jangovar encampment of Urûshoba has been nothing but trouble for the people of the Dale-lands and should be dealt with once and for all.
You have destroyed many siege engines and banners in the Jangovar encampment of Urûshoba. Your efforts will ensure the safety of all those who dwell in the Dale-lands.
